Package org.activebpel.rt.wsdl.def

Classes that represent WSDL elements (partner links, port types, properties, and the like) and that serialize and deserialize them.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
IAeBPELExtendedWSDLConst This interface defines several String constants used commonly throughout this package.
IAeBPELWSDLExtensionIOFactory Interface for factory that provides the wsdl4j impls for reading/writing bpel extensions to wsdl
IAePartnerLinkType This interface represents a Partner Link Type element.
IAePortType This interface represents a Role's PortType element.
IAeProperty This interface represents a Message Property extention element.
IAePropertyAlias This interface represents a Message Property Alias extention element.
IAeRole This interface represents a Partner Link Type's Role element.
IAeStandardSchemaResolver Implementors of this interface will resolve "standard" or "well known" schemas given the namespace of the schema.
 

Class Summary
AeBindingUtils Utilities for extracting info from WSDL bindings
AeBPELExtendedWSDLDef Read, write, modify and create BPEL Extended WSDL documents.
AeBPELWSDLExtensionIOFactory Factory for creating reader/writer entries in the WSDL serializers
AeBPELWSDLExtensionIOFactory.AeBaseImpl Base impl handles our classes and QNames
AeBPELWSDLExtensionIOFactory.AeBPEL4WSImpl BPEL4WS impl
AeBPELWSDLExtensionIOFactory.AeWSBPELImpl WSBPEL impl
AeFaultMatcher Utility class that determines the proper Fault defintion for a given port type, operation and input data.
AeMessageMatcher Provides a routine for matching a Document[] against wsdl messages to see if the message parts match the array.
AeOperationSignatureMatcher Utility class that finds an operation given a WSDL for the port type and the Document[].
AePartnerLinkTypeImpl This class represents an implementation mapping to a Partner Link Type extension within a WSDL document.
AePartnerLinkTypeIO This class serializes and deserializes a Partner Link Type extension implementation.
AePortTypeImpl This class represents a Role's PortType element.
AePropertyAliasImpl This class represents an implementation mapping to a Message Property Alias extension within a WSDL document.
AePropertyAliasIO This class serializes and deserializes a Message Property Alias extension implementation.
AePropertyImpl This class represents an implementation mapping to a Message Property extension within a WSDL document.
AePropertyIO This class serializes and deserializes a Message Property extension implementation.
AeRoleImpl This class represents a Partner Link Type's Role element.
AeStandardSchemaResolver This implemenation of a standard schema resolver knows how to resolve standard schemas from within the context of the AWF Designer.
AeWSBPELPartnerLinkTypeIO Reads and writes a partner link type def for WS BPEL 2.0
AeWSBPELPropertyAliasIO Reads and writes WS BPEL property alias elements
AeWSBPELPropertyIO Reads and writes WS BPEL property elements
AeWSDLExtensionIO Base class for reading/writing BPEL WSDL extensions elements
AeWSDLExtensionLoader Populates an extension registry with IO objects for reading and writing WSDL extensions to and from a WSDL document.
AeWSDLPrefixes WSDL prefix helper utilities.
